title: MS-Series SEALED metal toggle circuit breaker
text:
This article was posted on 10/09/2015 MS-Series SEALED metal toggle circuit breaker The MS-Series sealed, toggle circuit breaker is ideally suited for harsh environments and COTS military applications. Performance Highlights: 1-3 poles; 0.02-30 amps; 65VDC, 240VAC, 120/240VAC; MIL-PRF-39019F Ingress Protection; MIL-PRF-55629 and MIL STD 202 compliant; compact design; UL, cUL recognized & TUV pending.
